$ docker exec ant-clickhouse clickhouse-client --query "SELECT engine FROM system.tables WHERE database='ant' AND name='md_bars_buffer'"
Buffer

## Buffer Config in clickhouse_writer.go

    FlushInterval time.Duration // 默认 500ms
    MaxBatchSize  int           // 默认 10000
    QueueSize     int           // 默认 50000；满则走 spill

Default values confirmed:
    FlushInterval: 500 * time.Millisecond,
    MaxBatchSize:  10000,
    QueueSize:     50000,

ENV override: ANT_CH_BUFFER_QUEUE_SIZE, ANT_CH_BUFFER_MAX_BATCH, ANT_CH_BUFFER_FLUSH_MS

## md_ticks sorting_key (ADR-0008 §2.2 compliant)
